*** Settings ***
Library    RequestsLibrary

*** Variables ***
${BASE URL}    https://reqres.in/api
${USER ID}    1

*** Test Cases ***
Test All Users
    [Documentation]    Test GET All Users endpoint
    ${response}    Get Request    ${BASE URL}/users
    Should Be Equal As Strings    ${response.status_code}    200

Test User Info
    [Documentation]    Test GET User Info endpoint
    ${response}    Get Request    ${BASE URL}/users/${USER ID}
    Should Be Equal As Strings    ${response.status_code}    200

Test Create User
    [Documentation]    Test POST Create User endpoint
    ${request_body}    Create Dictionary    name=Yourname    job=Your Position
    ${response}    Post Request    ${BASE URL}/users    json=${request_body}
    Should Be Equal As Strings    ${response.status_code}    201

Test Update User
    [Documentation]    Test PATCH Update User endpoint
    ${request_body}    Create Dictionary    name=Your nickname    job=Your Position
    ${response}    Patch Request    ${BASE URL}/users/${USER ID}    json=${request_body}
    Should Be Equal As Strings    ${response.status_code}    200

Test Delete User
    [Documentation]    Test DELETE Delete User endpoint
    ${response}    Delete Request    ${BASE URL}/users/${USER ID}
    Should Be Equal As Strings    ${response.status_code}    204
